E_D("replace into `ecs_weixin_corn` values('70','a:3:{s:6:\"touser\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"msgtype\";s:4:\"text\";s:4:\"text\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";s:492:\"普遍来说，绿茶和黄茶是公认为所有茶类中最鲜嫩的茶类，且经过揉捻，浸出物出来得快，盖碗冲泡的时候，放差不多刚好覆盖满盖碗底部的量就可以了。\r\n\r\n不过要记住两点，一是不要盖上盖子，会把茶汤闷坏；二是太烫的水会伤害到绿茶和黄茶的茶叶，让茶汤变苦变涩，但又不能太低，使茶叶的香气激发不出来，一般常用的是90℃的水，可能会根据实际情况作出微调。\";}}','1471223290','1471223290','2','0','1');");
E_D("replace into `ecs_weixin_corn` values('71','a:3:{s:6:\"touser\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"msgtype\";s:4:\"news\";s:4:\"news\";a:1:{s:8:\"articles\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:10:\"article_id\";s:3:\"136\";s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"如何使你的茶具更健康\";s:7:\"content\";s:3600:\"<p><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 36px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 18px/32px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　一般很多人都会用钢丝球(清洁球)或是丝瓜等比较粗糙的清洗工具来刷洗茶具，这样是可以起到清洗的效果，但试想一下用这些比较粗糙的工具来清洗你的茶具，会很容易伤害茶具表面的釉质，使之变得越来越薄。慢慢地，这些茶垢就会完全渗入到茶具里面，那样茶具就会变成茶汤的颜色了，而且怎么也清洗不掉了。</span></p><p><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 36px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 18px/32px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 18px/32px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　最好的清洗方法是在每次喝完茶后，记得把茶叶倒掉，把茶具用水清洗干净。能够长期保持这种良好习惯的话，什么清洗工具都不用，茶具则可以保持明亮光泽。但有很多朋友都是喝完茶后就去休息或是做别的事情，清洗茶具的事情就忘记了，等到下次品茶的时候再来清洗茶具。这样经过长时间的浸泡，很多茶具都上了茶色，用清水是洗不掉的。这个时候，可以挤少量的牙膏在茶具上面，用手或是棉花棒把牙膏均匀地涂在茶具表面。大约过一分钟后再来用水清洗这些茶具，这样，茶具上面的茶垢就很容易被清洗干净了。用牙膏清洗，不会损坏茶具或伤害手，既方便又简单，茶友们都可以试试看。</span><br style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 18px/32px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"/><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 18px/32px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　茶具上的茶垢愈厚，泡出来的茶不见得愈健康或是香纯。常会听爱泡茶的老人家拿出心爱的茶壶，乌黑油亮的茶垢，似乎茶垢愈厚愈值钱。茶垢对人体健康是极为不利的。因此，爱喝茶也应该勤于刷洗茶具，才是良好的生活习惯。</span><br style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 18px/32px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"/><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 18px/32px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　（记者祝田园整理）</span></span></p>\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"file_url\";s:0:\"\";}}}}','1471310839','1471310839','2','0','1');");
E_D("replace into `ecs_weixin_corn` values('72','a:3:{s:6:\"touser\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"msgtype\";s:4:\"news\";s:4:\"news\";a:1:{s:8:\"articles\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:10:\"article_id\";s:3:\"138\";s:5:\"title\";s:52:\"好茶适宜淡品 大量喝浓茶对身体有害处\";s:7:\"content\";s:10890:\"<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\"><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　【</span><span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">一道茶网 茶文化</span><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">】小编在泡茶的时候经常会遇到“众口难调”的问题。茶叶太淡，有些人认为茶之无味，茶叶太浓，有的人会认为又苦又涩，甚至爱喝浓茶的人和爱喝淡茶的人分为两大帮派互不服气。那作为泡茶人，我们应该如何去判断茶的味道是越浓越好还是越淡越好呢？</span></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 16px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 16px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" dir=\"ltr\"><img style=\"FLOAT: none\" title=\"d30178744646476183c620b61ad77825_th.jpg\" src=\"http://www.chaligou.com/includes/ueditor/php/../../../images/image/42711471937223.jpg\"/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 16px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WORD-WRAP: break-word; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 26px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">　　喝茶</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WORD-WRAP: break-word; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 26px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">　　小编认为，虽然众口难调，但还是淡茶为好。茶汤味道的浓淡，有一部分是取决于茶碱与芳香物质的含量。不管茶碱的浸出含量有多少，都是有提神醒脑的效果的，而且所含的营养物质并不低于浓茶。但如果喝大量的浓茶，会很容易刺激神经，导致精神高度兴奋、引起失眠的状况，对身体也非常的不利。</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 16px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 16px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img style=\"FLOAT: none\" title=\"f6d6d4a7c0134f87b28255aaece7cf53_th.jpg\" src=\"http://www.chaligou.com/includes/ueditor/php/../../../images/image/46361471937223.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WORD-WRAP: break-word; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 26px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">　　喝浓茶对身体不利</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WORD-WRAP: break-word; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 26px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">　　许多茶友喝茶都有一些年头了，淡茶已经满足不了他们的口味，才渐渐地钟爱起浓茶。可能是日常生活的辣食口味，会让人觉得口重，认为浓饮才够刺激，毕竟喝茶追求的是茶的</span><a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; COLOR: rgb(0,112,192); FONT-SIZE: 16px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-DECORATION: underline; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" href=\"http://www.edaocha.com/baike/20151107/27932_1.html\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">滋味</span></a><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">。但从茶叶成分来说，</span><a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; COLOR: rgb(0,112,192); FONT-SIZE: 16px; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; TEXT-DECORATION: underline; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" href=\"http://www.edaocha.com/baike/20151107/27907_1.html\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">茶氨酸</span></a><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">含量越高，茶的甜度与鲜爽度就越高，苦涩度越低，顺滑度高，就会让你觉得味淡了，但这种淡是茶叶质量好的表现，味浓了，茶的真味反而会被其他物质夺走，这就是我们所说浓茶夺香的道理。</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 16px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 16px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WORD-WRAP: break-word; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 26px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">　　茶宜淡品</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WORD-WRAP: break-word; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 26px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">　　虽然浓茶满足了许多口味比较重的茶友，但小编不提倡喝浓茶，经常喝浓茶，会特别容易刺激胃。因为茶叶中大量的茶碱浸出后会刺激胃黏膜，会造成胃酸分泌过多的情况。所以一般情况下有胃溃疡和十二指肠的患者是一定要忌饮浓茶的，尤其是女性在生理期或孕期的时候，更是要忌饮浓茶。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WORD-WRAP: break-word; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 26px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">　　茶友中喜欢喝浓茶的也占了一大部分，但小编提倡，茶虽好，易淡品，从我们自身的健康考虑，一些对喝茶有所误解的茶友们，要清楚的了解正确喝茶的科学性，我们应该要尽量避开浓茶，选择淡茶。</span></p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WORD-WRAP: break-word; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 26px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16px\">　　（文/鹿与茶）</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"WIDOWS: 1; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 16px/26px 微软雅黑, 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"file_url\";s:0:\"\";}}}}','1471937319','1471937319','2','0','1');");
